Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.49,0:21:51.35,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}请回想起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.92,0:22:03.02,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}那温暖的脸颊上滑落而下的泪之请愿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.74,0:22:09.62,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}为何你在颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.74,0:22:15.18,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}现在寻求着何物？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.00,0:22:21.81,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}只有你无论多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.56,0:22:27.50,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}都想与你相拥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.62,0:22:33.88,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}蔚蓝的星海
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.02,0:22:39.76,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}波浪间漂浮的羽毛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.87,0:22:45.82,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}渐渐逝去的悲痛是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.89,0:22:51.40,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}向着明日的祈祷


